{"tid":1128831,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】33台灣人抵港擬參與遊行 遭入境處強制遣返","createTime":"2019-04-28T05:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T11:33:17.000Z","uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c46015c37df65e244873c1635f9a22bb403beb","tid":1128831,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:54:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-33%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E9%2581%25A3%25E8%25BF%2594-141700050.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%2525E9%252580%252583%2525E7%25258A%2525AF%2525E6%2525A2%25259D%2525E4%2525BE%25258B-33%2525E5%25258F%2525B0%2525E7%252581%2525A3%2525E4%2525BA%2525BA%2525E6%25258A%2525B5%2525E6%2525B8%2525AF%2525E6%252593%2525AC%2525E5%25258F%252583%2525E8%252588%252587%2525E9%252581%25258A%2525E8%2525A1%25258C-%2525E9%252581%2525AD%2525E5%252585%2525A5%2525E5%2525A2%252583%2525E8%252599%252595%2525E5%2525BC%2525B7%2525E5%252588%2525B6%2525E9%252581%2525A3%2525E8%2525BF%252594-141700050.html&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8k6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=b6f66710\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-33%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E9%2581%25A3%25E8%25BF%2594-141700050.html</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣明日發行反對《逃犯條例》修訂遊行，有33名台灣宗教團體人士昨日飛抵香港，計劃參加遊行，卻遭入境處拒絕入境並強制遣返。處方回覆傳媒查詢時指，在處理每宗入境個案時，均會依據法律和既定入境政策，考慮個別個案的情況後，作出批准或拒絕入境的決定。<br />\n據台媒報道，陸委會今日表示，已向港府表達關切，並要求港府應尊重並理性看待台灣人合法表達意見；又指香港辦事處當時並未接獲台灣人相關協助請求，但知悉事件後，已即洽航空公司了解情況，並對事件表示遺憾；強調台港交流向來緊密，希望港府能善待持合法證件入境的台灣人。<br />\n資料顯示，過往已有台灣人被拒入境香港的事件，例如去年台獨樂團「閃靈樂團」獲邀來港演出、2017年台灣學者吳叡人及吳介民教授申請赴港簽證被拒、台灣傳媒人張鐵志亦被拒入境等。"},{"pid":"852a7403f723a18f74c4bd4cf700bb2b6c7307bf","tid":1128831,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89a7f9e4277c648101326e641f8b81bd296e2c36","tid":1128831,"uid":105507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"乜撚野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a72a670a9f9e0bebd17a10a374166d5421f609","tid":1128831,"uid":220721,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:28:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"845a3527b52e6ced837581a37cac3452a4e442d4","tid":1128831,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"中國(入境處)"}]}